\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces OpKAN information flow across three decoupled layers. The HMM does not know about the KAN; the topology agent does not know about the PDE; the GPU training loop never waits on the LLM. Dashed arrows are asynchronous (bounded queues; maxsize=1 for inputs, maxsize=32 for outputs). The full training throughput of 26,300\,smp/sec is measured during sustained 5-epoch training; the standalone E2E validation suite reports 6,506\,smp/sec under a 50-step cold-start microbenchmark (see Section~\ref {sec:rq6}).}}{8}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:architecture}{{1}{8}{OpKAN information flow across three decoupled layers. The HMM does not know about the KAN; the topology agent does not know about the PDE; the GPU training loop never waits on the LLM. Dashed arrows are asynchronous (bounded queues; maxsize=1 for inputs, maxsize=32 for outputs). The full training throughput of 26,300\,smp/sec is measured during sustained 5-epoch training; the standalone E2E validation suite reports 6,506\,smp/sec under a 50-step cold-start microbenchmark (see Section~\ref {sec:rq6})}{figure.1}{}}
